<p>
I&#39;m still a bit sad about Flash going away. Yes, I know lots of people hated it. But it was an amazing tool for quick prototypes.  There are some projects that I keep revisiting, and over time I&#39;m converting them to HTML5.
</p>

<p>
Last year I converted my <a href="https://simblob.blogspot.com/2022/06/procedural-tree-generator.html" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">Flash procedural tree generator</a> (succeeded) and attempted to convert my <a href="https://www.redblobgames.com/x/2216-spaceship-flyer/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">Flash spaceship flyer</a> (failed). This time I wanted to run my Tank Control prototype from 2012:
</p>

